description: Modern two bedroom, two bathroom condominium with private balcony space and a deeded, heated garage parking space located in the heart of South Boston. Brand new construction in 2019, this luxurious home is walking distance to Seaport, the Red Line, and just a half mile to the beach. This unit features an open floor plan with gleaming hardwood floors, a gorgeous kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and a large kitchen island with quartz countertops. The primary bedroom features a large ensuite bathroom with a glass shower, as well as walk-in closets. The large second bedroom is located in the opposite wing of the home, adjacent to a full second bathroom that includes a bath tub. The Gribaudo is a professionally-managed elevator building with low condo fees, conveniently located one block from shopping and dining on East Broadway. First showings at open houses Saturday, April 12th from 12-2pm and Sunday, April 13th from 12-2pm.
